    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Nice comments @samouss 👍 I have a few questions remarks:\r\n - ok if the the connectPriceRanges makes more let's go for it\r\n - do you suggest to remove the inputs in the price ranges?\r\n - ok for changing the name. However I would still alias the new names to the old so that we don't introduce a breaking change here, add a deprecation notice and drop the deprecated names when we move to a new major version.",
